PolyOps is a Rust port of the Martinez-Rueda polygon clipping algorithm based on
the JavaScript reference implementation `martinez-polygon-clipping` by
Alexander Milevski (https://github.com/w8r/martinez), itself derived from:

    F. Martinez, A. J. Rueda, F. R. Feito.
    "A new algorithm for computing Boolean operations on polygons."
    Computers & Geosciences 35 (2009) 1177-1185.
    (extended in 2013)

